# Listing System

This rule defines the functionality for listing and selling accounts.

## Core Components
[commands.js](mdc:commands.js)
[interactions.js](mdc:interactions.js)

## Key Features
- `/list` command for creating new account listings
- "Purchase Account" button functionality
- "More Information" button to show detailed account info
- "Mark as Sold" button for staff to mark accounts as sold

## Key Functions
- `listCommand` in commands.js
- `handleListButtons` in commands.js
- `ephemeralFlowState` for storing listing details
